Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…你到底做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.67,0:00:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王啊 愚蠢的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让臣子去杀害女王是多么残酷的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那因愤怒而颤抖的肩膀 岂能示诸于众
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王啊 我不会要求你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会要求仰慕追随着你的骑士 对同胞兵刃相向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那边的王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然已陷入疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够代替疯狂的王 领导人民的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了你别无他人 难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王啊 请下决断
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您揭竿而起 令人尊敬的勇敢女王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克服洗脑 跟随女王的正义之士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够为狂王的暴政画下句号之人 正是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.32,0:01:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三势力的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么空是以那个为目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了吧 不战而胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,300)\pos(133,329)\an7\3c&H4F0999&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\shad0\fs26\fsp5\be5}国王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(320,300)\pos(102,309)\an7\3c&H4F0999&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\shad0\fs17\fsp3\be5}Grandmaster
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不战而胜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若非拥有此等智慧之人 便无法拯救此时的艾尔奇亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们「人类种」在「迪司博德」是最弱种族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(274,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可正因如此 我们要考虑如何跟强者较量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要磨练智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有拥有此等智慧之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因最弱 才明白自身的强大…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并非追求鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如人民所愿 没错 我们追求的是和平
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军 协助红色女王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开包围
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不许死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这群卖国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以红色棋子为盾…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 对方是曾经一起作战的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们无法轻易下手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 竟然压制住了「森精种」的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(518,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底找的哪个种族做帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是把这个国家交给那些人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 疯狂的王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在现实战争中 有时候不用杀死王也能分出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没有胜算了 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…不战而胜的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说投降？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会把这个国家交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的国家是我们自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全军 牺牲自己也要砍下敌军首级
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把卖国贼全部杀掉 前进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱敌被逼上绝路 就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不行 不战而胜什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:39.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会这么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴政 恐怖支配 独裁者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪个时代 这种执政者的「末路」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何都十分相似
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被身边某个甚至不是士兵的人暗杀致死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 我们的世界可没有这里这么美好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各种纷争 互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们比你更加经验老道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场比赛 空白获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷我一直相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.63,0:06:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会有这样的人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因最弱 才明白自身强大…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因最弱 才能与真正的强者较量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是「人类种」的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也是可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合你哦 史蒂芬妮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你爷爷相信着的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信着「人类种」的你的爷爷没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(351,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就不会被称为愚王了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 真的很感谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空 白…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖啦 乖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们用了什么骗术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗术？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想说单凭「人类种」就战胜了「森精种」的魔法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(590,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确想这么说 而且这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么疑问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算借助「森精种」的魔法来帮助「人类种」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(668,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(333,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话是个不错的战略
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我很不爽你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有「森精种」大人庇护的话就无法生存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(288,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不觉得太卑躬屈膝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「人类种」有「人类种」的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(288,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,437)\fs21}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你直到最后都怀疑我们是他国的间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们才赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人类怎么可能和魔法对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你怎么想 这就是你的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论对手是「森精种」还是神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(455,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』没有败北二字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(333,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太小看人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到「森精种」的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(392,437)\fs21}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再毁掉约定 你知道要订下多麻烦的契约吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.94,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有小看啊 我可是认真的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 你把女孩子弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明连女朋友都没有 明明还是个处男
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:09.89,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不承认…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我宣布这场选拔赛的最终获胜者是空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有人要向他挑战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.86,0:09:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 谨遵先王遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空将加冕为新国王…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是空 而是『    』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(504,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个人在一起才是『    』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(576,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王是我们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 这办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「十条盟约」规定需指定全权代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能是两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那按照分工 形式上该由我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反对！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥当上了国王就能建后宫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会不要白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形式上的国王应该是白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没异议了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 那么重新…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反对！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂等等啊 我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然会开玩笑 真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道要下枪雨了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白超认真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会手下留情哦 我的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.35,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)\shad0}三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一胜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:37.08,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多该认输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连胜两盘才算赢 是哥提出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么国王只能一个人当啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 「十条盟约」第七条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集团纠纷应指定全权代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本就没说只能是一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像花了不少时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为你们的疏忽才会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.14,0:11:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸好红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种暴露程度至于脸红吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没让她穿内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特意说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我穿成这样想干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\pos(95,96)\fs21}前国王的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\pos(470,100)\fs21}史蒂芙以前的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的衣服这么寒酸真不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 这种明显看得出真空状态的二次元演出也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些 要请你们开始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有国王期间 内政完全停滞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内政就由史蒂芙来处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 都已经裸装打了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要用陷阱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效率优先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 由于艾尔奇亚日渐衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有传闻某些大臣和他国勾结…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为新国王 不能被他们有机可乘…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请各位向盟约宣誓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行猜拳 然后故意输给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出剪刀 各位出布
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,败者禁止一切虚伪报告和随意性传达情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来利用盟约 这样就能使间谍消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么来吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「向盟约宣誓」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(424,437)}Assent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所见 我国的粮食问题极为严重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就实行我接下来的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农业方面…我们要导入轮种式农业
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将农田统一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小麦→根类作物→大麦→牧草
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照以上顺序耕种
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国债是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详情我等会告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发行国债让银行购买 以此作为预算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来让我们坐等成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你究竟是何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能这么轻松地处理内政
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩文明帝国我也喜欢一口气处理完内政
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像个笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把猜谜游戏专用资料书籍事先输入进去真是做对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是外挂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在有魔法这种官方外挂的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别把这个称为外挂好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 终于到了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真的打算以这副打扮出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 还是这身衣服最令我安心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去去便回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 你在紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 你不是也有人群恐惧症吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时压抑着而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬爱的国民…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 各位「人类种」同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(444.166,437)}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们「人类种」奉行着「十条盟约」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(318.166,437)}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个没有战争的世界屡战屡败
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅剩下最后的都市——艾尔奇亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此发问 这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为先王失败了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是第十六位种族？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们无法使用魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是因为命运注定我们会灭亡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过去远古的大战中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸神 「森精种」「兽人种」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(382,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(533,437)}Warbeast
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在众多种族之争中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也曾战斗过 并且存活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去这整片大陆都被人类国家所占领 这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是擅长暴力的种族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不像「森精种」能使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(408,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有「兽人种」的那种身体能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(363,437)}Warbeast
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不如「天翼种」那样长寿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(407,437)}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却能支配整个大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我们特别强化了战斗技能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之所以能战斗并存活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我们是弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论在哪个时代 哪个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者磨练利齿 弱者磨练智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们为何会被逼至这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为受「十条盟约」约束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者失去利齿 学会了磨练智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本是我们弱者专属的智谋 战略
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有生存的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今强者全都具备了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才导致现在的这种惨状
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何垂头丧气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再问一次 为何垂头丧气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去如此 今后也将如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们根本没有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强者模仿弱者得来的武器 无法发挥出真正实力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我们武器的本质在于…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自卑产生的软弱与怯懦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因怯懦 我们有逃离魔法的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因怯懦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拥有从「学习」和「经验」得来的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能够预测未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再次重复
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪个时代 咬破恃强怠惰之人咽喉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我们这些高傲的「弱者」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在此宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:17:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加冕为第二百零五代艾尔奇亚国王和女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.53,0:17:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是赐予全权代理人的…种的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「种的棋子」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们二人在此宣言 会以弱者的身份生存
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以弱者的方式战斗 并且以弱者的方式消灭强者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去如此 今后也将如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认吧 我们是最弱的种族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们生来一无所有 因此我们能成为任何事物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以身为最弱种族为傲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也受够痛苦了吧 也厌倦卑躬屈膝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了 各位「人类种」同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(521,437)}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 我们艾尔奇亚向全世界国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,点起反击的狼烟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回我们的国界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你你…你都干了什么好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要这么惊讶吗 受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史蒂芙 好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我怎么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣战什么的 你打算毁灭这个国家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是让你稍微学会怀疑别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他国会怎么看待我们战胜「森精种」这一事实？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(515,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们受到了比「森精种」更强种族的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(409,437)}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 在他们弄清楚我们背后的种族之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会按兵不动？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 为了让全世界陷入疑心猜忌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以刻意宣战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们却什么也不做 养精蓄锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都想到了这一步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(409.533,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人的话 说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从狭小的游戏房间到破旅店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是史蒂芙的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是国王寝室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许这里最令人静不下心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「天翼种」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(424,437)}Flugel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有长久的寿命与高魔法适性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活在漂浮于天空的巨大幻想种--「阿邦特·赫伊姆」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(437,437)}Fantasma
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有强烈的求知欲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了收集全世界的书本而进行游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉能拉拢他们成为同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有异世界的知识这一诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发 发生了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情变得有趣起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称神的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是自称 我就是真正的神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有特图这个名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的世界感觉如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品味还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想让我们那边的旁观主义者神明大人也学学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人是魔法师 我们却用不了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领土仅剩下一座城市 形势令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而『    』不允许失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(364.5,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来叫你们过来真是没错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我基本上也是旁观主义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会刻意偏袒某个种族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 之前我也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界一切都由游戏决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说唯一神的宝座也是由游戏决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十六种族也是特意为此而设
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国际象棋一方的棋子也是十六个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 称霸所有种族才有权利挑战神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊 脑袋转得这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种适应速度 实在看不出来是刚从异世界来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你还笑得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「无论何种游戏都要到达顶点」是我们的信条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 我料定你们一定会来获得挑战我的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 忘记之前的棋局输给了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不会再有下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我特图就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…特图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:21:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前没有输过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏之神首次败北之后非常不甘心而把我们叫来这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思 为什么你会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.56,0:22:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我能体会那种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『    』没有败北
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs21\pos(363,437)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以彼此为对手 却互相输了无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不允许赢了就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然选择你们是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 不允许赢了就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次赢的将会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是理由 失望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是拯救人类这种高尚的理由让我安心多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 特图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你让我们重生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里才是属于我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神明大人 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.99,0:23:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久后再见 下次是在棋盘上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特 特图…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空 白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是特图 那位唯一神吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.81,0:23:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.11,0:23:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说曾经赢过他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先让我们下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在基于形式之美就让我这么开头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「很久很久之前…」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先称霸世界 然后目标是打败神明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.73,0:23:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在请听我诉说最新的神话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚应该很快活对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 玩了一整晚的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,362)\3c&HD000CA&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\shad0\fs33\fsp5\be7}布局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.04,0:23:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(699,322)\3c&HD000CA&\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord3\shad0\fs17\fsp3\be7}Weak Square
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:55.83,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,回り続ける歯車には成り下がらない
Comment: 0,0:01:56.13,0:02:02.63,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,平均を演じる　誕生から始まった地獄
Comment: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:07.33,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,遊び半分で　神が導いた盤上の世界
Comment: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:09.23,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,ノー　ノー　ノーゲーム　ノーライフ
Comment: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:12.43,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,ぬるい平穏をバッサリ切り捨てて
Comment: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:16.53,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,栄光への階段に存在刻むんだ
Comment: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:21.03,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,目に映るのは完全勝利の運命
Comment: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:25.03,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,何もかも計算通り
Comment: 0,0:02:25.13,0:02:29.93,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,変えてやる　染まらない『　』で
Comment: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:36.53,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,We are maverick 救済なんていらない
Comment: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:39.83,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな理不尽　襲おうとも
Comment: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.33,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,勝てばいいだけの話だろう
Comment: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:49.53,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,駆け引きと才能が無敗誘う
Comment: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:55.33,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,生まれ直した命で楽しむさ
Comment: 0,0:02:56.13,0:03:03.13,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,自分だけは自分信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:55.88,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不甘沦落为转动不停的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:02:02.68,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}平凡的人生 从降生之初便是无尽地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:07.38,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}视同儿戏般 去往神明所指引的棋盘世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.28,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}No No No game no life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.48,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}彻底抛弃无趣的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:16.58,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}在通往荣光的阶梯上 刻下存在的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:21.08,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}完全胜利的命运已清晰可见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:25.08,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一切尽在掌控之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:29.98,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}以纯洁无瑕的『空白』改变命运
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:36.58,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We are maverick 何需那虚伪的拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.88,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无论遭遇何种不公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:43.38,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只需要取得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:49.58,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}凭借才能谋略 立于不败之地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:55.38,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}以重生般的姿态 体验全新的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:03.18,OP2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}必须对自己深信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:43.35,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}誰にも言えない孤独を抱えたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.82,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}一人で泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:53.96,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}誰にも上手に笑えない僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:57.78,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}二人出会って　笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:03.97,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}真夜中過ぎに　想像の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:09.20,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}どうしようもない気持ちをただ押しやって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:14.86,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}さよなら　僕らはきっと生まれ変われるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:18.89,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}悲しみに手を振るんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:20.57,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}そしていつか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:23.08,ED1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be9}空っぽなままの心に
